Package java.util.spi

Added Classes and Interfaces
CalendarDataProvider An abstract class for service providers that provide locale-dependent Calendar parameters.
CalendarNameProvider An abstract class for service providers that provide localized string representations (display names) of {@code Calendar} field values.
ResourceBundleControlProvider An interface for service providers that provide implementations of java.util.ResourceBundle.Control.
 

Changed Classes
LocaleServiceProvider

This is the super class of all the locale sensitive service provider interfaces (SPIs).
TimeZoneNameProvider An abstract class for service providers that provide localized time zone names for the TimeZone class.
